File in java
-File class in java is a representation of file and directory
-since in different environment there is different format of directory and file a simple
 string name is not the replacement therefore this file class is introduced in java.
-It has several method which helps to do so many operation to the file or to the directory such as renaming the file 
 deleting the file ,listing the content of the folder or the directory.
 -It is an abstract representation of file and directory.
